    <h3>About Me</h3>
    Hi there, I’m a Newcastle University student studying computer science. I’ve been programming since 2014 with a strong background in Python as well as Java, C#, C and HTML/CSS since starting my degree. I’ve always enjoyed programming and have completed a variety of personal projects that are available to see on my Github or here on the projects page. I’m always looking to expand my programming skills within a professional environment and improve my skills in the workplace. I’m always looking for more freelance and contract work and I'm interested in full time positions too. Since the pandemic, I have started running my own tutoring business where I have tutored 5 different clients in Python programming for the last two years.
    <figure>
