    </figure>
    <br>
    <br>
    Some of my favourite projects have utilised frameworks like Flask, PIL, Evol, spaCy alongside datascience libraries such as Numpy, Pandas and matplotlib. I'm open to learning new frameworks and I'm confident in my ability to pick-up new frameworks and languages quickly. I'm a self-starter who links to take the initiative and get started. I try ensure I properly plan and design before starting projects, but I often find that getting stuck in and experimenting is the best way for me to learn! Please enjoy this lovely new website and have a look around some of the cool projects I've been working on these past few years!
